{"tid":491031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蕭若元爆電視台陳姓高層 女藝人面前手淫","createTime":"2017-12-06T06:29:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T06:55:56.000Z","uid":70985,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0a75beb98af0a7366d0e829c88e29573739262d9","tid":491031,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T06:29:14.000Z","msg":"一向盛傳娛圈有「潛規則」，最近荷李活爆出電影大亨Harvey Weinstein曾性侵犯及性騷擾多位影星，女星Alyssa Milano喺網上發起「#MeToo」，鼓勵曾被性侵犯及性騷擾嘅女星一齊發聲，令事件引起全城關注。<br />\n<br />\n昨日有周刊指，香港娛圈都有類似情況，蕭若元同白韻?講出電視台陳姓高層嘅往事，蕭若元稱「潛規則」嘅風氣喺大陸最盛行，佢話曾經有一個選美嘅佳麗同電視台陳姓高層北上公幹，電視台陳姓高層夜晚飲到醉晒去咗佳麗間房拍門，仲拎滅火筒撞門，想破門而入，最終佳麗搵警衛；呢位電視台陳姓高層又試過同一個女藝人傾工作，載咗個同事去荒山野嶺，話自己有性衝動，喺女藝人面前手淫。<br />\n<br />\n報道又話白韻琹就爆有電視台高層向候選佳麗暗示「陪瞓」可以做冠軍，據知早年選美曾有高層搵候選佳麗叫佢哋「識做」就會晉級，事件都驚動成個台，要搵人調查為保形象，低調處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20171206/20236487\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171206%2F20236487&d=06gfd3pA%2Fau4FvtBh%2FCmGi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=5c3fc0a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171206%2F20236487&h=122a5869\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20171206/20236487</a><br />\n<br />\n#metoo"},{"pid":"9ae62759f371cf29585f6c858f01a9d69939a8cc","tid":491031,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T06:34:20.000Z","msg":"蕭生好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XNgVsZ5DFcA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXNgVsZ5DFcA&d=06gfd3pA%2Fau4FvtBh%2FCmGi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=09f9ada0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XNgVsZ5DFcA</a>"},{"pid":"807f71a5d927980a53cd74b0332255eddf6d633a","tid":491031,"uid":4879